sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / KServe Proxy
    participant MM_Local as ModelMesh Instance A<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant MM_Remote as ModelMesh Instance B<br/>8033/TCP Thrift/gRPC
    participant RT_Local as Model Runtime A<br/>8085/TCP or UDS
    participant RT_Remote as Model Runtime B<br/>8085/TCP or UDS
    participant Controller as modelmesh-serving<br/>Controller

    Note over Client, RT_Remote: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (model loaded locally)
    Client->>MM_Local: POST inference request<br/>gRPC :8033 | TLS + mTLS (optional)
    MM_Local->>etcd: Lookup model location<br/>gRPC :2379 | TLS (optional)
    etcd-->>MM_Local: Model record (loaded on Instance A)
    MM_Local->>RT_Local: Forward with injected model ID<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS | No TLS (localhost)
    RT_Local-->>MM_Local: Inference result
    MM_Local-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client, RT_Remote: Flow 1b: Model Inference Request (model loaded remotely)
    Client->>MM_Local: POST inference request<br/>gRPC :8033 | TLS + mTLS (optional)
    MM_Local->>etcd: Lookup model location<br/>gRPC :2379 | TLS (optional)
    etcd-->>MM_Local: Model record (loaded on Instance B)
    MM_Local->>MM_Remote: Forward inference request<br/>Thrift/gRPC :8033 | TLS + mTLS
    MM_Remote->>RT_Remote: Forward with injected model ID<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS | No TLS (localhost)
    RT_Remote-->>MM_Remote: Inference result
    MM_Remote-->>MM_Local: Response
    MM_Local-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Controller, etcd: Flow 2: Model Registration and Loading
    Controller->>MM_Local: registerModel<br/>gRPC :8033 | TLS + mTLS
    MM_Local->>etcd: Store model record<br/>gRPC :2379 | TLS
    MM_Local->>RT_Local: loadModel<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS | No TLS
    RT_Local-->>MM_Local: Model loaded (size, status)
    MM_Local->>etcd: Update model status = LOADED<br/>gRPC :2379 | TLS

    Note over MM_Local, etcd: Flow 3: Model Eviction (LRU Cache Full)
    MM_Local->>RT_Local: unloadModel<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS | No TLS
    RT_Local-->>MM_Local: Unload confirmed
    MM_Local->>etcd: Update model record (unloaded)<br/>gRPC :2379 | TLS
